1.2.0 2026-06-09
 - Background stats refresh via cron (bin/rt-admin-dashboard-refresh)
 - Stats stored as RT::Attribute on System object; survive Apache restarts
 - Mason pages read from attribute; fall back to direct queries on first run
 - Remove per-process in-memory cache (<%once> TTL pattern)
 - All DB queries consolidated into RT::Extension::AdminDashboard::collect_stats()

1.1.0 2026-06-02
 - Internationalize all UI strings; add translations for 37 languages
 - Switch all loc() msgids to English; German and other languages via po/

1.0.0 2026-06-02
 - Initial release
 - Replace RT admin page with live statistics dashboard
 - Ticket stat cards with counter animation
 - User info card with progress bars
 - Configuration info card (Queues, Custom Fields, Groups)
 - Admin menu as responsive icon-card grid
 - Per-process 10-minute query cache
 - Theme-aware via Bootstrap 5 CSS variables
